# APIMirrorPulse - Bulk API Health Tracker

APIMirrorPulse monitors large batches of APIs and reports live status and timing results.

## Features
- Logs status + latency  
- Retry and timeout handling  
- Tabular CLI output  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_APIMirrorPulse.git
cd 22_APIMirrorPulse
python monitor.py
